      "span_text": "The derivation of the complete equations of motion is quite a complicated challenge. Following Ref. [CITATION_1] , we separate the variations with respect to each field into those corresponding to occurrences via Ω (−) a b , that we will call implicit, and the rest, that we will call explicit: "
